 punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>progressText<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>1 / 5<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>right-button-wrapper<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>icon-button<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>nextButton<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>➡️<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"css-스타일링\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css-%EC%8A%A4%ED%83%80%EC%9D%BC%EB%A7%81\" aria-label=\"css 스타일링 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS 스타일링</h2>\n<p>네비게이션 컨트롤을 그리드 레이아웃을 사용하여 배치하고, 버튼 스타일을 설정한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.page-navigation-controls</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1fr auto 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">align-items</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin-top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1.5rem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">max-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 400px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> relative<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1rem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.left-button-wrapper</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">justify-self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> flex-start<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.right-button-wrapper</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">justify-self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> flex-end<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.icon-button</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">cursor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pointer<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.icon</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 24px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 24px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>여기서 중요한 부분은 <code class=\"language-text\">grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;</code>이다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">1fr</code> : 첫 번째, 세번째 열(왼쪽 버튼, 오른쪽 버튼)이 가변 크기를 가지며, 공간이 있으면 확장된다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">auto</code> : 가운데 열(페이지 진행률 표시)은 내용 크기만큼 유지된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>이렇게 하면 왼쪽 버튼과 오른쪽 버튼이 화면 크기에 따라 확장되면서 가운데 열은 고정된 크기를 유지한다. 이 방법은 레이아웃이 유연하면서도 왼쪽이나 오른쪽 요소가 사라지는 경우에도 레이아웃이 깨지지 않는다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"가운데 정렬된 네비게이션 혹은 헤더 grid로 구현하기","date":"February 01, 2025"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/css/가운데-정렬된-네비게이션-혹은-헤더-grid로-구현하기/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/회고/테오의-스프린트-18기-참가-후기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"테오의 스프린트 18기 참가 후기"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/react.js/zustand의-shallow-comparison으로-최적화하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Zustand의 shallow comparison으로 최적화하기"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"],"slicesMap":{}}